  "933": {
    "inputs": {
      "text": "A punk rock woman in her 30s stands full body on a rain-soaked industrial rooftop at night, centered in the frame, facing directly toward camera, with the distant stormy city skyline behind her and red antenna lights blinking on communication towers to the right. She has messy bleach-blonde shaggy hair with dark roots, heavy smoky eye makeup, deep red lipstick, layered silver necklaces, a black cropped leather jacket covered in small pins and metal studs, a leopard-print corset top, tight black jeans with a studded belt and hanging chains, and black heeled ankle boots reflecting in shallow puddles. A wired handheld microphone is in her right hand, the black cable trailing across the wet concrete in front of her feet.\n\nShe begins singing with intense rock-performance energy, lifting the microphone to her mouth as her lips clearly move in sync with the vocals. Her left hand grips the belt chain, then rises toward the camera in a sharp expressive gesture. Wind blows her textured hair across her face and makes the leather jacket ripple. Rain mist drifts sideways across the rooftop, puddles shimmer with red and blue city reflections, and steam rises from vents in the background. She takes one small step forward while staying centered, shoulders squared, eyes locked on the lens, performing with fierce confidence.\n\nThe shot starts as a wide full-body view showing her boots, microphone cable, rooftop ledge, antennas, satellite dish, and storm clouds. The camera slowly dollies forward in a smooth cinematic push-in, moving from full body to knees, then waist, then chest, finally ending in a tight close-up of her face as she sings directly into the microphone. Use a gritty cinematic music-video style, high contrast, cool blue moonlight from the storm clouds, red warning lights glinting on wet black leather, soft backlight outlining her hair, shallow depth of field increasing as the camera moves closer. Audio: powerful female rock vocals clear and upfront, faint rooftop wind, distant thunder, light rain hitting concrete, and subtle city ambience underneath.\n",
      "output_mode": "string"
    },
